Deployed multiple Windows Servers within a VMware environment to emulate a comprehensive company infrastructure. Key services implemented included Active Directory for managing users and groups, IIS for web services, FSRM for storage management, Work Folders for file synchronization, DNS for hostname resolution, DHCP for dynamic IP assignment, ADCS for certificate management, and ADFS for single sign-on and federated identity management. These components collectively provided a robust and realistic infrastructure, facilitating various administrative, operational, and security functions.
Grade: A
